Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_CLI_5.0.0_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator CLI 5.0.0 - 16 September 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46239635\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator CLI 5.0.0 - 16 September 2015</h1>\n    <p>Appcelerator CLI 5.0.0 is a major release, introducing new features, improvements and bug fixes. This release of the Appcelerator CLI includes version 4.2.0 of the NPM package and version 5.0.0 of the Core package.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239635_AppceleratorCLI5.0.0ReleaseNote-ComponentVersions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Component Versions</span></h2>\n    <p>The following components are shipped with CLI 5.0.0:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Name    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Version    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \"><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/appcelerator/alloy/releases\" target=\"_blank\">Alloy</a></strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">1.7.8 (update)</strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Arrow Builder    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>1.2.48    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Arrow Cloud CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>1.0.26    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \"><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium/releases\" target=\"_blank\">Titanium CLI</a></strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">5.0.3 (update) </strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239635_AppceleratorCLI5.0.0ReleaseNote-NewFeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New Features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Support to create, build, run and package watchOS applications    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>New <tt class=\" \">appc info</tt> command to display development environment information    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>New <tt class=\" \">appc switch org</tt> command to switch between organizations without logging in and out of the CLI    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239635_AppceleratorCLI5.0.0ReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-624\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-624</a>: Platform-SDK: Logout request is incorrect    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-648\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-648</a>: appc setup continues to show latest Ti SDK installed even after it has been deleted    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-708\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-708</a>: Login token flag is not removed    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-731\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-731</a>: Error when publishing app    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-747\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-747</a>: Node processes are getting orphaned in certain cases    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-749\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-749</a>: If you do &quot;appc ti sdk select &lt;SDK_VERSION&gt;&quot;, a &quot;Failed to run command sdk&quot; error message will appear    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-755\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-755</a>: Cannot run appc commands with CLI 4.2.0-5+    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-756\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-756</a>: When you create an Apple Watch app, &#xAE; trademark appears after Apple    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-774\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-774</a>: Support for WatchOS2 project in appc    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-760\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-760</a>: Project creation prompts for App ID; --id not supported    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-768\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-768</a>: Alloy app fails to build on window&apos;s with error &quot;Alloy compiler failed&quot;    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-786\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-786</a>: Creating an Apple WatchOS2 app crashes if selected SDK is pre-5.0    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-792\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-792</a>: Regression running project    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-809\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-809</a>: Cannot create Apple Watch App from Appc CLI    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46239635\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator CLI 5.0.0 Release Note"});